title: Complete the Square
text: Group and factor: $$4\left(x^2-6x\right)$$ + $$\operatorname{36}\left(y^2-10y\right)$$ $$=$$ $$-864$$. Then complete the square.

title: Divide to Get Standard Form
text: After completing the square: $$\frac{\left(x-3\right)^2}{9}$$ + $$\frac{\left(y-5\right)^2}{36}$$ $$=$$ $$1$$. Identify a $$=$$ $$6$$, $$b$$ $$=$$ $$3$$.
